# Commande /scan — Design System Real Estate UI

## Fichier Figma de référence

- **URL** : https://www.figma.com/design/9ZjzJGJ07zCiTHMpbXB2j2/%E2%9C%85-Real-Estate-UI?node-id=123-1523&t=EuysFBsqzXqIXR7O-1

